Source: bunsen-utilities
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: John Crawley <john@bunsenlabs.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-systemd (>= 1.5), help2man
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://github.com/BunsenLabs/bunsen-utilities
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/BunsenLabs/bunsen-utilities.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/BunsenLabs/bunsen-utilities.git

Package: bunsen-utilities
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bunsen-common, python2.7, python-gtk2, python-xlib, yad, wmctrl, xdotool (>=1:2.20110530.1-3), libnotify-bin
Conflicts: bunsen-lock, bunsen-user-setup, bunsen-wmhacks
Recommends: bunsen-exit (>=9.1-1), bunsen-conky, gmrun, light-locker, openbox, tint2, nitrogen | feh, scrot
Description: Small scripts to use with BunsenLabs.
 A collection of small scripts to provide various functions
 which might be useful to BunsenLinux users and system administrators.
 .
  - bl-conky-session: Script to handle multiple conky sessions.
  - bl-conkyedit: Script to find and edit conky config files.
  - bl-conkypin: Script to assist the relocation of conky windows.
  - bl-conkyzen: Yad-based conky manager.
  - bl-hotcorners: Script to add hot corners to Openbox.
  - bl-kb: Script to manage keyboard shortcuts.
  - bl-lock: Script to lock the display.
  - bl-obthemes: Script to save or restore openbox gui configurations.
  - bl-package-versions: Utility to display the versions of BunsenLabs packages.
  - bl-tint2-session: Script to handle multiple tint2 sessions.
  - bl-tint2edit: Script to find and edit tint2 config files.
  - bl-tint2restart: Script to restart all running tint2 processes.
  - bl-tint2zen: Yad-based tint2 manager.
  - bl-xinerama-prop: Script to get xinerama properties in a shell script.
  - bl-notify-broadcast: Script to send user notifications from root processes.
